  m_text: When a player empties their hand all other dominos in all other players
    hands get added up and rounded to the nearest multiple of 5 then added to the
    score of the round winners team. Same thing happens in a draw when no players
    can make any moves. Exept the winner is the player with the lowest value dominos.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
